# Tix Mix themes

Mario Party–inspired minigame title cards for the ticket shuffle intro. Original artwork only — do not copy Nintendo assets, fonts, or trademarked characters.

## Reference material

- `docs/TIX-MIX-THEMES.md` — theme vocabulary (volcano, neon, beach, space, etc.)

- `graphics/tix-mix/` — finished title-card artwork ready to wire into the app

- `graphics/_staging/` — WIP/experiment title cards (ignored by Cursor index; move to `graphics/tix-mix/` when ready)

## Visual direction

- Strong thematic identity per card (background motif, border treatment, title typography)

- Match the existing neon arcade palette in `app/style.css` where cards appear in-app

- Title cards are decorative overlays — keep performance and readability in mind

## Integration

When wiring a theme into the shuffle intro, coordinate with the shuffle minigame rule (`SHUFFLE_*` timing, intro clip keys in `playShuffleIntroClip`).
